sentences: Fumina Hara (原 史奈, Hara Fumina, born 22 May 1981 in Tokyo, Japan) is a Japanese actress and gravure idol.
She has played the role of Usagi Tsukino in the Sailor Moon musicals, and has gone on to a varied career.
She has played the love interest in Aishiteruze Baby.
She was married to former football player Tetsuo Nakanishi from 2007 to 2014.
